---
const pageUrl = new URL("/support", Astro.site);
const ogImageUrl = new URL("/assets/og-card-v1.png", Astro.site);
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Support — Sidemesh</title>
<meta name="description" content="Get help with Sidemesh. Common issues, setup guidance, and how to reach us." />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#e9edf0" />
<meta property="og:title" content="Support — Sidemesh" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Get help with Sidemesh. Common issues, setup guidance, and how to reach us." />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:url" content={pageUrl.toString()} />
<meta property="og:image" content={ogImageUrl.toString()} />
<meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
<meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
<meta property="og:image:alt" content="Sidemesh — agent workstation control from anywhere." />
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImageUrl.toString()} />
<meta name="twitter:image:alt" content="Sidemesh — agent workstation control from anywhere." />
<meta name="twitter:site" content="@mukhtharcm" />
<meta name="twitter:creator" content="@mukhtharcm" />
<link rel="canonical" href={pageUrl.toString()} />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/favicon.png" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=Manrope:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
  :root {
    --paper: #e9edf0;
    --ink: #101616;
    --ink-soft: #323d3c;
    --muted: #65706f;
    --line: rgba(16, 22, 22, 0.14);
    --surface-solid: #fafcf7;
    --sage: #2e7666;
    --wrap: min(1220px, calc(100% - 40px));
    --ease: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; text-size-adjust: 100%; }
  body {
    min-height: 100dvh;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  a { color: var(--sage); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .wrap { width: var(--wrap); margin: 0 auto; }
  .nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    background: rgba(233, 237, 240, 0.78);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16, 22, 22, 0.08);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 22px;
    min-height: 76px;
  }
  .brand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .brand-logo {
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(16, 22, 22, 0.12);
  }
  .nav-back {
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 9px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: color 180ms var(--ease), background 180ms var(--ease);
  }
  .nav-back:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    background: rgba(250, 252, 247, 0.56);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  main { padding: 48px 0 96px; }
  h1 {
    font-family: "Instrument Serif", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  p, ul { color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 16px; }
  ul { padding-left: 22px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card {
    background: var(--surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .card p { margin: 0; }
  .section { max-width: 720px; }
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 24px 0 48px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--muted); }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .nav-inner { min-height: 64px; }
    main { padding: 32px 0 64px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/">
        <img class="brand-logo" src="/assets/app-icon.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" />
        Sidemesh
      </a>
      <a class="nav-back" href="/">← Back</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <div class="section">
      <h1>Support</h1>
      <p>Quick answers to common questions and how to get in touch if you need more help.</p>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Getting started</h3>
        <p>Install the daemon on a trusted host with <code>sidemesh setup</code>, then open the app and scan the pairing QR code or add the host manually. The app will connect directly to your host over your private network.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>The app cannot reach my host</h3>
        <p>Make sure your device and host are on the same network or connected through Tailscale. Verify the daemon is running with <code>sidemesh status</code>. Check that the host address and token in the app match what the daemon printed during setup.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Notifications are not arriving</h3>
        <p>Enable notifications for Sidemesh in iOS Settings → Notifications. Background sync also requires Background App Refresh to be enabled. The app checks for updates periodically when in the background.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Live Activities are not showing</h3>
        <p>Live Activities require iOS 16.1 or later. Make sure they are enabled in Settings → Sidemesh → Live Activities. They appear when an agent session is active.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Contact us</h3>
        <p>For bugs, feature requests, or security concerns, open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/mukhtharcm/sidemesh/issues">GitHub</a> or reach out through your existing private channel.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="wrap">
    <span>© Sidemesh</span>
    <nav aria-label="Footer">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
    </nav>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
